@startuml CEDR_Security_Story_Pyramid
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor<<Abuse>> #FF6B6B
    BackgroundColor<<Countermeasure>> #FFE66D
    BackgroundColor<<Security>> #4ECDC4
    BackgroundColor<<Functional>> #95E1D3
    BackgroundColor<<NonFunctional>> #F38181
}

left to right direction

rectangle "NON-FUNCTIONAL\n(3 Stories)\nSystem Support" as NF <<NonFunctional>> #F38181

rectangle "FUNCTIONAL\n(6 Stories)\nCore Features" as FUNC <<Functional>> #95E1D3

rectangle "SECURITY\n(5 Stories)\nImplement Controls" as SEC <<Security>> #4ECDC4

rectangle "COUNTERMEASURE\n(5 Stories)\nPrevent Attacks" as CM <<Countermeasure>> #FFE66D

rectangle "ABUSE CASES\n(5 Stories)\nBlock Attackers" as ABUSE <<Abuse>> #FF6B6B

NF --> FUNC
FUNC --> SEC
SEC --> CM
CM --> ABUSE

note right of ABUSE
    **Total: 24 User Stories**
    
    Security Coverage:
    • Authentication (MFA)
    • Authorization (RBAC)
    • Encryption (AES-256)
    • Integrity (Hash Chain)
    • Non-Repudiation (HSM)
end note

note bottom of NF
    US-NF-001: Performance
    US-NF-002: Data Retention
    US-NF-003: Cross-Platform
end note

note bottom of FUNC
    US-F-001: Real-Time Alerts
    US-F-002: Evidence Retrieval
    US-F-003: Fleet Correlation
    US-F-004: OTA Logging
    US-F-005: Health Dashboard
    US-F-006: Compliance Reports
end note

@enduml
